<TEXT>
 <PERSON> David </PERSON> <PERSON> Crary </PERSON>, news editor at the <ORGANIZATION> AP </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> bureau </ORGANIZATION> in <LOCATION> Johannesburg </LOCATION>, has been reporting from <LOCATION> Africa </LOCATION> since 1985.
